## Public non-fork repos by category

### Art

* [Mapsmash](http://github.com/bryanlandia/mapsmash) - A few projects abusing the Google Static Maps API to remix geography
* [Twiggish](http://github.com/bryanlandia/twiggish) - A generative twig-like drawing AS3 project

### Plone

* [getpaid.firstdata](https://github.com/bryanlandia/getpaid.firstdata) - Plone GetPaid payment provider

### Me
I'm online at http://www.woollyandwise.com, on LinkedIn at http://linkedin.com/in/bryanwilsonseattle, and tweet once in a blue moon at http://twitter.com/bryanlandia
